org.eng.aisp.classifier

Class TrainingSetInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eng.aisp.classifier.TrainingSetInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<TrainingSetInfo.LabelInfo>

    public class TrainingSetInfo
extends Object
implements Iterable<TrainingSetInfo.LabelInfo>, Serializable
    Contains information about a set of ILabeledDataWindows. Information includes
    • total number of samples
    • total milliseconds of sampled data
    • label names present
    • for each label name
      • the set of label values present
      • for each label value
        • the total number of samples
        • the total number of sample milleseconds.
    Author:
    dawood
